Will running a `trackCustomBehavioralEvent` like below automatically display the event properties for the event in the activity feed? Does anything else need to be done within HubSpot to start seeing the properties populate?
```_hsq.push(["trackCustomBehavioralEvent", {
        name: "Test Event",
        properties: {
            experience_id: '12345',
            event_property_desc: 'This is event an event property'
       }
    }]);```
